      • main

        public static void main​(java.lang.String[] args)
        Creates an object of type CSVParser which parses a CSV file. If the format of the CSVParser is valid, creates a Country object from each parsed line. Tests the Country class using with various date ranges. For each test case, either prints that data for the overlapping years found or catches an IllegalArgumentExceptions.
